
@h1 Using a timer synchronously
See <a href="http://www.boost.org/doc/libs/1_55_0/doc/html/boost_asio/tutorial/tuttimer3.html">http://www.boost.org/doc/libs/1_55_0/doc/html/boost_asio/tutorial/tuttimer1.html</a>


@felix
